    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You look the target in the eye and attempt to send it such horrifying visions that it suffers a short mental breakdown. The subject falls @Condition[prone]{prone} and starts laughing in a manic, humorlous manner for 1d4 rounds, unable to take any action or think about anything. A creature incapable of laughter will simply make random sounds or speak gibberish.<br><br>For 2 rounds after this behavior fades, the subject becomes @Condition[shaken]{shaken}.</p>\n\n\n\n",
